XianGe Stage0 build scripts: build tools for XianGe Linux system.

steps:
	1. make an empty work directory, such as "/mnt/xg" or "~/xg"
	2. decompress file to work directory
	3. enter "stage0" of work directory
	4. run ./download
	5. after all packges download ok, run ./build, with root priviledge.
	6. wait build ok
	7. then you'll get the all tools in /tools direcotry, and a list of installed packages in /tools/installed.log


	if you have any question or sugestion, please mail to Zhang Lihui<swordhuihui@gmail.com>
 
